overview: The BDK continues their all-out assault on CHIKARA when Lince Dorado, Pink Ant and Daizee Haze face The Colony in trios action, Claudio Castagnoli and Ares wrestle the Throwbacks, and Eddie Kingston battles the massive Tursas! Player Uno looks to avenge his partner's defeat by challenging for the Young Lions Cup.
title: CHIKARA The Mint Condition
